FBIS4-18778 "drweu069_l_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-069 Daily Report 6 Apr 1994 SPAIN 'Arafat: Spain Might Take Part in Observer Force 'Arafat: Spain Might Take Part in Observer Force LD0604162994 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network in Spanish 1600 GMT 6 Apr 94 LD0604162994 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network Spanish BFN [Excerpt] Spain might take part in the international observer force due to be deployed in Hebron. This was announced by PLO Leader Yasir 'Arafat after his meeting with the Spanish Foreign Minister Javier Solana. According to the Palestinian leader, Spanish participation will be decided upon if there is no quick agreement for Italian participation. [passage omitted]
